{
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 100,
      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "markdown", "showLineNumbers": false },
        "content": "# Assignment 2 — SLI / SLO\n\n| SLI | SLO target | Recording metric |\n|-----|------------|------------------|\n| Availability | ≥ **99%** | `sli:availability:percent` |\n| Latency (p95) | ≤ **200 ms** | `sli:latency:p95_milliseconds` |\n| Error rate | ≤ **1%** | `sli:error_rate:percent` |\n| Success rate | ≥ **99%** | `sli:success_rate:percent` |\n\nDashed lines = SLO thresholds. Generate traffic via the Shop Portal to see live changes.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Overview",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "id": 101,
      "title": "SLI vs SLO (time series)",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-main" },
      "description": "Share of microservices with successful Prometheus scrape (up=1). SLO: ≥ 99%.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "dashed+area" }
          },
          "decimals": 2,
          "max": 100,
          "min": 95,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 99 },
              { "color": "transparent", "value": 99 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percent"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "min", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-main" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sli:availability:percent",
          "legendFormat": "Availability (aggregate)",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "up{job=~\".*-service\"} * 100",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "vector(99)",
          "legendFormat": "SLO 99%",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "title": "SLI: Availability vs SLO (≥ 99%)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-main" },
      "description": "HTTP request latency p95 across services. SLO: ≤ 200 ms.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "dashed+area" }
          },
          "decimals": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "transparent", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 200 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "ms"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sli:latency:p95_milliseconds",
          "legendFormat": "Latency p95 (aggregate)",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (service, le) (rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[1m]))) * 1000",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}} p95",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "vector(200)",
          "legendFormat": "SLO 200 ms",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "title": "SLI: Latency p95 vs SLO (≤ 200 ms)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-main" },
      "description": "Failed business operations / total attempts. SLO: ≤ 1%.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "dashed+area" }
          },
          "decimals": 2,
          "max": 5,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "transparent", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 1 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percent"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sli:error_rate:percent",
          "legendFormat": "Error rate",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "vector(1)",
          "legendFormat": "SLO 1%",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "SLI: Error rate vs SLO (≤ 1%)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-main" },
      "description": "Successful business operations. SLO: ≥ 99%.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "dashed+area" }
          },
          "decimals": 2,
          "max": 100,
          "min": 95,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "transparent", "value": 99 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percent"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 12 },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "min"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sli:success_rate:percent",
          "legendFormat": "Success rate",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "vector(99)",
          "legendFormat": "SLO 99%",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "SLI: Success rate vs SLO (≥ 99%)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 20 },
      "id": 102,
      "title": "HTTP traffic (request rate)",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus-main" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 25,
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "normal" }
          },
          "unit": "reqps"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 21 },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (service) (rate(http_request_duration_seconds_count[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Request rate by service (drives SLI movement)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    }
